Package: skylight
Type: Package
Title: A simple sky illuminance model
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: c(person(
               family = "Hufkens",
               given = "Koen",
               email = "koen.hufkens@gmail.com",
               role = c("aut", "cre"),
               comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5070-8109")),
             person(given = "BlueGreen Labs",
              role = c("cph", "fnd"))
               )
Maintainer: Koen Hufkens <koen.hufkens@gmail.com>
Description: A simple sky illuminance model which calculates values (in lux) 
 for both sun and moon. The model is a verbatim translation of the code 
 included in `Computer Programs for Sun and Moon Illuminance With Contingent 
 Tables and Diagrams by Janiczek and DeYoung published in the US Naval 
 observatory circular nr. 171, 1987.
URL: https://github.com/bluegreen-labs/skylight
BugReports: https://github.com/bluegreen-labs/skylight/issues
